snippet.title: Dragon Ball Z Budokai Tenkaichi 1 - Opening (4K HD)
snippet.description:
Straight up one of the best videogame openings. 

Also, this is the non-Japanese version. The Japanese version uses We Gotta Power, and honestly this version is miles better.

DBZ Budokai Tenkaichi, a PS2 game from 2005 for those who don't know.
